reviewText: This vhs was funny, educational and I enjoyed the artists that I had never seen in person or in video sing their hits.  Very entertaining.
product seems satisfactory. I don't understand why you have to have to write a book to describe how you feel about something. Is this enough words?.
If you love classic country music, this is a must!!  You won`t be sorry. Something you will go back to many times!!
We are big fans of the older country music.  We invited a bunch of friends over and everyone enjoyed this video.
The quality of the sound and the picture is grest.  If you wan to see some legends performs just lioke the original sound, buy this vhs.
